          "description": "Dr. Nicholas is an outstanding doctor. My husband had knee surgery with him 20 years ago, and recently I had the opportunity to be treated by him as well. I had a complex meniscus tear and was experiencing significant pain. When I first saw Dr. Nicholas, I expected a long wait before surgery, but to my surprise, it was scheduled just three days after my initial appointment.\n\nOn the day of surgery, I anticipated long delays, as is often the case in hospitals, but everything ran right on schedule. The level of professionalism was exceptional. Dr. Nicholas and his entire team were organized, courteous, and highly professional throughout the process.\n\nI am extremely grateful to Dr. Nicholas and his team and would highly recommend them. Shanika provided excellent service at check-in, my pre-op nurse Rimma was supportive, polite, and attentive, and PACU nurse Judith was incredibly helpful and had me ready and organized in no time.",
